description: The final part of the Upload series finds Derek Atlas inviting over porn star Jimmy Durano for his personal cam show. Derek greets the fans tuning in for this personalized show and asks them what they want to see. The fans have spoken and they want to see Jimmy fuck Derek. The amount of chemistry between Jimmy and Derek make this an easy decision for Derek, who accepts the challenge given by the fans tuning in for the show. They look at each other and smile, excited that they are just about to start the show.
title: Upload Part 3
